{"tid":1452255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日機場要人！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:35:06.000Z","uid":256673,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"157f336589fdd6dd7ec804775b3eda274257a081","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:36:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dMGgpeV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdMGgpeV.jpg&h=748e23c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VFtfmB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VFtfmB.jpg&h=586c9298&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/083612_779a9942e05124904efe1d5e140a615f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F083612_779a9942e05124904efe1d5e140a615f.jpeg&h=144e28b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/12/083612_7fcf56a9dcb0dd2d5ee4e888b640e789.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F12%2F083612_7fcf56a9dcb0dd2d5ee4e888b640e789.jpeg&h=bd85c093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相信大家都會認同811是無比憤怒同難過的一晚，同時相信明天亦會出現一連串不合作運動<br />\n<br />\n我地呢度主力為812迫爆機場作宣傳以及發布相關消息。<br />\n <br />\n812我們將挑戰AA的底線，請大家發揮你地既創意，提出並盡力實現可行嘅行為藝術，務求將最真實既一面帶俾抵港旅客睇，盡量以 不爭執、不破壞 為基礎。<br />\n<br />\n所以麻煩各位，唔好再玩接機，笑笑口和理非，要記住個女仔半面係血嘅樣；記住班黑警係一米距離內開槍同掉人落電梯；記住自己呢刻係幾咁憤怒<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家義憤填膺，但大家要明白到，機場係一個結界，不能衝擊，雖然極度憤恨，但我們亦有理性，可以和平表達訴求！請各位812準時一點正，以和理非既極致去討回公道!<br />\n<br />\n同時亦請大家要將矛頭對準政權，唔好俾警察轉移到視線！<br />\n<br />\n我地既目標，係要令到政府出黎正視民眾！！<br />\n<br />\n毋忘初心 五大訴求 缺一不可！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示：<br />\n<br />\n1. 口號<br />\n唔好再嗌圍爐口號（香港人加油）<br />\n保持憤怒，統一口號<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n2. 服飾<br />\n大家記得一定要帶衫換，一定要戴口罩，全民blackbloc，保障自己保障他人<br />\n（關於gear, 請大家自行決定帶與否）<br />\n<br />\n3. 為防因太多人一齊搭交通工具，盡早出門，可以就朝早去到<br />\n<br />\n4. 到機場請自由發揮，目標係要塞爆機場，唔要圍爐式集會<br />\n<br />\n5. ！全民糾察！唔要大台，唔好比人騎刧運動<br />\n<br />\n7. 請自備乾糧、替換衣物、充電器、拖板等日用品<br />\n<br />\n8. 文宣唔嫌多！印得幾多得幾多！<br />\n<br />\n9. 有projector嘅朋友亦可帶嚟播片畀全世界知香港發生咩事！<br />\n有手足已有projector, 仲爭腳架同藍牙喇叭<br />\n（如有人有12v外置充電器更好，for 三腳插，咁就可以長期播放）<br />\n<br />\n10. 離開機場前請換好衫，盡量結伴同行，切勿落單<br />\n<br />\n見到有人衝禁區要立即阻止<br />\n我地目標唔係塞禁區，係塞禁區外面<br />\n一衝禁區，一定出實彈<br />\n一衝禁區，一定出實彈<br />\n一衝禁區，一定出實彈<br />\n一衝禁區，一定出實彈<br />\n一衝禁區，一定出實彈<br />\n<br />\n最後，請提防有臥底潛伏在身邊<br />\n<br />\n祝各位好運，香港人加油"},{"pid":"33416aac28dbaba4500a6c27da82c37d0a5c3341","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:19.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"e1c1c2a16c759820b0fe5f641f60b7b2f62e6b47","tid":1452255,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9cf0f3074c2251662070b580634216a3205e2a1","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"c833ff5e51509f58a982be9c578aad6cf00fe16f","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c337adebd7157a63f83a98a94a2ae014bbb1f175","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:38:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"29da083dcfd7bbe59789d8588079c7b00e4e9ade","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:39:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d0b5f730ab0df23a42fc5a314c16916ce590c03","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7db237d667ea0de95ce14943b454bf358ff7d06b","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:45:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"71c56bec96df0dfb8b5f188b6bf534a6f85178cd","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:06:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e396cd1c104fe1a49d1a38baeefaa3289b8a52b","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9af470efe6395d7739ff6276bb5ab49f4daf1d12","tid":1452255,"uid":167467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:54:25.000Z","msg":"【幫手推】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請帶備更換衣物及梳洗用品入機場</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451296</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5e88a543c91097f56113e21becd738b6eec436d3","tid":1452255,"uid":256673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52dd7e0c36a1e0ae5705da800db52298c97cc578","tid":1452255,"uid":296350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:31:14.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n<br />\n<strong>前線良心記者<br />\n求你哋連成一線，接力問落去<br />\n畀佢哋遊走咗，下一位就follow up question繼續問<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片<br />\n準備播放器，迫使cctvb要播<br />\n佢一路拒絕播嘅畫面出街</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？ 點證明 冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=09221e5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=348b41eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkcjWZIlHEnPb%2Ft7norCwxRo%3D&h=a94228b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?